\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Hari had found Yugo by chance eight years ago, just after arriving on Trantor, when he and Dors were on the run from Imperial agents. An hour's talk had shown Hari that Yugo was an untutore
d genius at trans-representational analysis. Yugo had a gift, an unconscious lightness of touch. They had collaborated ever since. Hari honestly thought he had learned more from Yugo than the other way around.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 

