\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "I shall have to turn most of the heavy lifting over to you, I fear." Hari deliberately put his feet up on his desk. Might as well look casual, even if he didn't feel that way. He envied Yugo's heavy-bodied ease.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "This First Minister stuff?"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "It is getting worse. I have to go see the Emperor again."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "The man wants you. Must be your craggy profile."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "That's what Dors thinks, too. I figure it's my disarming smile. Anyway, he can't have me."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "He will."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "If he forces the ministership on me, I shall do such a lousy job, Cleon will fire me."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Yugo shook his head. "Not wise. Failed First Ministers are usually tried and executed."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
