\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Yes, and we're psychohistorians. Seekers of predictability." Hari threw up his hands in exasperation. "Why doesn't that count for anything?"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Because nobody in the citadels of power has seen it work."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "And they won't. Once people think we can predict, we will never be free of politics."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "You're not free now," Yugo said reasonably.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Good friend, your worse trait is insisting on telling me the truth in a calm voice."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "It saves knocking sense into your head. That would take longer."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Hari sighed. "If only muscles helped with mathematics. You would be even better at it."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Yugo waved the thought away. "You're the key. You're the idea man."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Well, this font of ideas hasn't got a clue."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Ideas, they'll come."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "I never get a chance to work on psychohistory anymore!"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "And as First Minister\emdash "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
