\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Nowhere, without you."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "There will be some progress, Yugo. I am not vain enough to think everything depends on me."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "It does."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
