All were entirely proper and devoid of embarrassing challenge. No alarming art here, thank you. Nothing "disturbing" was even allowed in public places on Trantor which the Emperor might visit. By exporting to the periphs all hint of the unpleasantness an
d smell of human lives, the Imperium achieved its final state, the terminally bland.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
