Some figures clearly made fun of the }{\fs20 courtly}{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033  }{\fs20 gen}{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 try, as puffy caricatures}{\fs20  }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 of their ostentatious clothes and poses.
}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
