\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Parties are supposed to cheer people up," Yugo said, sliding a cup of }{\fs20  }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033  across Hari's smooth mahogany desktop.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
