\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "All that luxury, powerful people, beautiful women, witty hangers-on\emdash I think I could have stayed awake."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "That's what depresses me, thinking back over it. All that power! And nobody there seems to care about our decline."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Isn't there some old saying about\emdash "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
