\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Me either, but pomposity springs forth eternal. It looks comic in retrospect."}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Yugo moved restlessly around Hari's office. "So they don't care?"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
