\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Not possible. Boker wanted Faith, he gets all of it. " "Nonsense! Also, I demand you let me visit her and that odd metis charmant curiosity Garcon in the cafe\emdash 
at will. I've never known beings like either of them before, and they are the only society that I now have. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
