but the envelope was growing, an orange cylinder fattening in 5-space, billowing out under pressure from the (}{\fs20 quick skittering}{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033  tangles made; Emotion Agents interchanging packets at high speed, }{\fs20 
