\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Try a little humor, maybe. He thumbed back to pace and said, "If you give me a hard time, fella, I'm going to give her that scurrilous poem you wrote about her. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
