\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Wouldn't I! You'll be lucky if she ever speaks to you again. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 A canny smirk. "Monsieur forgets the Maid does not know how to read. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
