\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Voltaire glared, muttering, "Between Scylla and Charybdis... "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 What was that mind plotting, sharp as a scalpel? He\emdash or it\emdash 
was integrating into this digital world faster than any sim Marq had ever known. Once the debate was over, Marq vowed to strip that mind down and study its c
utting edges again, put its processor layouts under the 'scope. And there was that odd memory from eight thousand years ago, too. Seldon had been a bit odd about that....}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "I promise to produce la lettre if you will just let me see her once more. In return, you'll vow never to so much as mention 'La Pucelle' to the Maid. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
