\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Gar?on happened to know that the cook spent her three days a week off\emdash Garcon himself worked seven days a week\emdash in the corridors of the Louvre. "A}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
