air work, often carried out on an utterly unsanitized field. There were antimicrobial methods available to the humaniform robots that could not work for ordinary humans, she had said. He had no idea how this could be. She discouraged further discussion, o
ften deflecting him with passion. He had to admit that as a ploy this was completely effective.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
