\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "I gave it to three of those new research assistants, " Yugo said soberly, his Dahlite energies expended. "They couldn't make sense of it. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
