\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 One persistent heritage of pre-antiquity was the standard Galactic Year, used by all worlds of the Imperium in official business. Hari had always wondered: Was it a signature of Earth's orbita
l period? With its twelve-based year of twelve months, each of rwenty-eight days, it suggested as candidate worlds a mere 1, 224, 675 from the 25 million of the Empire.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
