\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 When the human lifespan reached those ranges, a destructive feedback began. Markets became jagged landscapes, peaking and plunging. Cultures lurched}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
