 a few centuries, chaos destroyed most of the bioscience capability, or else religious restrictions smothered it. The mean lifespan slid down again.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "How strange, " Hari said, observing the severe curves of the cycles, their arcs crashing into splin-}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
