\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Yugo grinned. "Look at the media\emdash plays, legends, holos. The very old are always ugly, greedy misers, trying to keep everything for themselves. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
