\par }{\fs20  "}{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 At least we can understand why most societies learn not to let people live too long. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Hari studied the event-surfaces. "Ah, but who learns?"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
