\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Sheelah looked dumbfounded. Dors had probably been operating under the assumption that the failure to bail out was a temporary error. It had lasted too}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
