\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 The door snicked open. An antechamber that he recognized. Ipan blundered into a chair and almost fell.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Hari made the lungs work hard. The gasping cleared his vision of the dark edges that had crept in, but the blue-white flies were still there, fluttering impatiently, and thicker.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He tried the far door. Locked. Hari summoned what he could from Ipan. Strength, power, joy.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Ipan slammed his shoulder into the solid door. It held. Again. And again, sharp pain\emdash and it popped open.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Right, this was i
t. The immersion bay. Ipan staggered into the array of vessels. The walk down the line, between banks of control panels, took an eternity. Hari concentrated on each step, placing each foot. Ipan's field of view bobbed as the head seemed to slip around on 
liquid shoulders.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Here. His own vessel.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Dors' tiktok was ready for him. It had seen him coming and latched itself to the board, covering the vital controls.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Ipan bent to the tiktok's punch panel. He jabbed at the keys, remembering the access code.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Ipan's fingers were too broad. They could not hit a single key at a time.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 The room of bleached light was getting fuzzy. He made Ipan try the code again, but the stubby fingers mashed several keys at once.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 The blue-white flies flapped at the edges of his vision. Ipan's hands whacked in frustration at the punch-pad.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Think. Hari looked around. Ipan wasn't going to last much longer. A desk nearby had a writing slate and pen.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Leave a note? Hope the right people find it...}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He made Ipan stagger to the desk, grasp the pen. An idea flickered as he tried to write: I NEED...}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He turned and tottered back to the capsule. Concentrate.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Gripping the pen, he punched down with the butt. It struck a key cleanly. The blue flies flickered in his vision.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 The access code was hard to remember now. He worked on it one number at a time. Stab, poke, jab\emdash  and it was done. A light winked from red to green.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He fumbled with the latches. Popped it open.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 There lay Hari Seldon, peaceful, eyes closed.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Emergency controls, yes. He knew them from the briefing.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He searched the polished steel surface and found the panel on the side. Ipan stared woozily at the meaningless lettering.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Hari himself had trouble reading. The letters jumped and fused together.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He found several buttons and servo controls. Ipan's hands were worse now. It took three stabs with the pen to get the reviving program activated. Lights cycled from green to amber.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Ipan abruptly sat down on the cool floor. The blue-white flies were buzzing all around his head and now they wanted to bite him. He sucked in the cool dry air, but there was no substance in it, no help...}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Then, without any transition, he was looking at the ceiling. On his back. The lamps up there were getting dark, fading. Then they went out.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 22.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
