The recovery program was still sending electro-stims through his muscles. He let them jump and tingle and ache while he thought. He felt fine. Not even hungry, as he usually did after an immersion. How long had he been in the wilderness? At least five day
s.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He sat up. There was no one in the vessel room. Evidently Vaddo had gotten some silent alarm but had not alerted anyone else. That pointed, again, to a tight little conspiracy.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He got out shakily. To get free he had to detach some feeders and probes, but they seemed simple}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20 enough}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Ipan. The big body filled the walkway. He knelt and felt for a pulse. Rickety.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 But first, Dors. Her vessel was next to his and he started the revival. She looked well.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Vaddo must have put some transmission block on the system, so
 that none of the staff could tell by looking at the panel that anything was wrong. A simple cover story: a couple who wanted a really long immersion. Vaddo had warned them, but no, they wanted it, so... A perfectly plausible story.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Dors' eyes fluttered. He kissed her. She gasped.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He made a pan sign, quiet, and went back to Ipan.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Blood was flowing steadily. Hari was surprised to find that he could not pick up the rich, pungent elements in the pan's blood from smell alone. A human missed so much!}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 

\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He took off his shirt and made a crude tourniquet. At least Ipan's breathing was regular. Dors was ready to get out by then, and he helped her disconnect.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "I was hiding in a tree and then\emdash poof!" she said. "What a relief. How did you\emdash "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Let's get moving, " he said.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
