\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Somehow her expression made him laugh. She was very rarely surprised.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "You did this?"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
