They were in a Council House near the palace, ringed by their guard parties. Lamurk had selected the room and its elaborate floral decorations. Usually it served as a lounge for representatives of rural-style Zones and so
 was lush with greenery. Unusually for Trantor, insects buzzed about, servicing the plants.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
