\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 As soon as Hari returned to Streeling, he went into seclusion. The pandemonium following Lamurk's assassination were the worst hours he had ever spent.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
