just as Daneel had predicted. Hari liked that aspect of the 
matter particularly: a prediction holding true. In the mob hysteria which followed, no one assumed he was implicated. Hari also knew his limits, and here they were. He could not deal with such chaos, except in the broader context of mathematics.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
