\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Yes, and will stop the invidious comparison of one year with the next. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Won't such a shift of the mean lose discriminatory power at the upper end of the distribution?" He narrowed his eyes.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "That is regrettable, but yes. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "It's a wonderful idea, " Hari said.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 She seemed surprised. "Well, we think so. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
