\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Set the statistics so that the average hitter strikes 500, rather than the hard-to-remember 446 of the present. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "But I don't think a principle of social justice\emdash "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
